{
  "title": "SCCM & SQL Applications - Service Health Overview",
  "description": "Application-focused dashboard for SCCM and SQL Server services, monitoring service health, application performance, and error events by role category. Basic configuration suitable for customization.",
  "template_variables": [
    {
      "name": "host",
      "prefix": "host",
      "available_values": [],
      "default": "*"
    },
    {
      "name": "role",
      "prefix": "role",
      "available_values": [
        "sccm-site-server",
        "sccm-sql-server", 
        "sccm-sql-reporting-server",
        "sccm-management-point",
        "sccm-distribution-point"
      ],
      "default": "*"
    }
  ],
  "layout_type": "ordered",
  "widgets": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "# üè¢ SCCM & SQL Applications Dashboard\n\n**Application and service health monitoring for SCCM infrastructure**\n\nüîß **Service Health**: Windows service status by role category  \nüóÑÔ∏è **SQL Performance**: Database and reporting service metrics  \nüåê **IIS Performance**: Web services for Management/Distribution Points  \nüìù **Error Events**: Application error monitoring by role  \n‚ö° **Performance**: Key application performance indicators  \n\n*Use template variables above to filter by specific hosts or roles*",
        "background_color": "vivid_blue",
        "font_size": "14",
        "text_align": "left",
        "vertical_align": "top",
        "show_tick": true,
        "tick_pos": "50%",
        "tick_edge": "bottom",
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "definition": {
        "type": "note",
        "content": "## üîß Service Health Monitoring",
        "background_color": "gray",
        "font_size": "18",
        "text_align": "center",
        "vertical_align": "center",
        "show_tick": false,
        "has_padding": true
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3,
        "width": 12,
        "height": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "definition": {
        "type": "check_status",
        "check": "windows_service",
        "grouping": "cluster",
        "group_by": ["host", "service"],
        "tags": ["$host", "$role", "state:running"],
        "title": "SCCM Services - Running",
        "title_size": "16",
        "title_align": "left"
      },
      "layout": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "width": 6,
        "height": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "definition": {
        "type": "check_status",
        "check": "windows_service",
        "grouping": "cluster",
        "group_by": ["host", "service"],
        "tags": ["$host", "$role", "state:stopped"],
